videos.description: Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree comes off the screen, rolls down low, Jermaine Samuels lobs him the ball, and he finishes with the two-handed slam.

videos.description: Saddiq Bey leaves barely any time left on the clock as he drains the deep three giving the Wildcats a 20-point lead going into the half.
